AttributeList.Text:
Valve Monitor monitors single acting valves with Energiseed only or De-energised only or both Feedback states. Selection of feedback states in use can be selected with Bits 0 and 1 of the "ControlWord" Input.
Control Word Bit 0 = IN_DE in use Bit 1 = IN_EN in use
Valve Monitor should be called within a Timed Interrupt OB and the duration counters should be multiplied by the Timed Interrupt Cycle time to get the durations in Seconds.
Note: If Activation State changes before destination FeedBack is reached then the Duration count is not moved to the Archive and therefore does not affect the average duration. (De)Activations Count(s) will be incremented
